---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="项目">
  <article class="article" data-fade>
    <header class="article-hero">
      <p class="article-eyebrow">Projects</p>
      <h1 class="article-title">项目</h1>
    </header>

    <div class="article-body">
      <div class="article-list">
        <a class="project-item" href="#floral">
          <img class="project-thumb" src="/cards/projects-card.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy" />
          <span class="project-item-text">
            <span class="project-item-eyebrow">Tool · 2026</span>
            <span class="project-item-title">花艺课程表海报</span>
            <span class="project-item-desc">改一处，全表自动重排。</span>
          </span>
        </a>
        <a class="project-item" href="#snow">
          <img class="project-thumb" src="/projects/snow/card.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy" />
          <span class="project-item-text">
            <span class="project-item-eyebrow">Interactive · 2026</span>
            <span class="project-item-title">湖心亭看雪</span>
            <span class="project-item-desc">把「上下一白」做成可以划进去的湖。</span>
          </span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>

  <article class="article" id="floral" data-fade>
    <header class="article-hero article-hero--sub">
      <p class="article-eyebrow">Tool · 2026</p>
      <h1 class="article-title">花艺课程表海报，从 4 小时缩到 1 分钟。</h1>
    </header>

    <div class="article-body">
      <p>
        工作室有两套花艺课程：零基础创业班和创业全能班。每次开新课，都要重做两张课程表海报发出去。之前用 PPT 或 Canva 做，一张海报 2-4 小时，两张就是半天。更麻烦的是每张海报里有 30 多处日期、5-6 个章节标题、100 多个技能点，改一处常常忘了另一处。
      </p>

      <p>
        把“内容”和“版式”分开。版式定好一次，以后只改数据。运营改一个开课日期，全表 30 多处日期一起更新；改一个章节名，罗马序号自动重排；两套课程共用一份数据源，重复内容不用抄两遍。
      </p>

      <p>
        两张海报从 4-8 小时变成 1 分钟。保存即可发。
      </p>

      <figure class="article-figure">
        <img
          src="/cards/projects-card.jpg"
          alt="零基础创业班与创业全能班课程表海报"
          loading="lazy"
        />
      </figure>

      <p>
        现在它只是一个内部工具，不是产品。我还在想：这种“重复劳动自动化”的小工具，能不能做成让更多花艺、教培、餐饮商家都能用的东西？
      </p>
    </div>
  </article>

  <hr class="project-divider" />

  <article class="article" id="snow" data-fade>
    <header class="article-hero article-hero--sub">
      <p class="article-eyebrow">Interactive · 2026</p>
      <h1 class="article-title">湖心亭看雪，把「上下一白」做成可以划进去的湖。</h1>
    </header>

    <div class="article-body">
      <p>
        张岱写雪，最妙是那几个量词：长堤一痕、湖心亭一点、与余舟一芥、舟中人两三粒。我用 AI 生成了一座三维的雪夜西湖，把这几个「一」做成可以划进去的场景。
      </p>

      <p>
        拖动环顾，空格或长按「划桨」行舟。大雪三日，湖中人鸟声俱绝，你一个人往湖心亭去。
      </p>

      <figure class="article-figure">
        <a href="/snow/" aria-label="进入湖心亭看雪互动场景">
          <img
            src="/projects/snow/card.jpg"
            alt="雪夜西湖：小舟驶向湖心亭"
            loading="lazy"
          />
        </a>
      </figure>

      <p>
        <a class="project-link" href="/snow/">独往湖心亭 →</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </article>
</Base>

<style>
  .article {
    max-width: none;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0 96px 0;
  }

  .article:last-of-type {
    padding-bottom: 160px;
  }

  .article-hero {
    padding: 160px 0 96px;
  }

  .article-hero--sub {
    padding: 96px 0 72px;
  }

  .article-eyebrow {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 22px;
    letter-spacing: -0.28px;
    color: #707070;
    margin: 0 0 16px 0;
  }

  .article-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 60px;
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 72px;
    letter-spacing: -1.2px;
    color: #000;
    max-width: 55ch;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .article-body {
    max-width: 768px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .article-body p {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 26px;
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 37.7px;
    letter-spacing: -0.26px;
    color: #000;
    margin: 0 0 0 0;
  }

  .article-body p + p {
    text-indent: 0;
    margin-top: 1.5em;
  }

  .article-body p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .article-figure {
    margin: 48px 0;
    width: 100%;
  }

  .article-figure img {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    display: block;
  }

  .project-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 32px;
    padding: 36px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #d0d0d0;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .project-item:first-child {
    border-top: 1px solid #d0d0d0;
  }

  .project-thumb {
    width: 192px;
    height: 128px;
    object-fit: cover;
    display: block;
    flex: none;
  }

  .project-item-text {
    display: block;
    min-width: 0;
  }

  .project-item-eyebrow {
    display: block;
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 20px;
    letter-spacing: -0.26px;
    color: #707070;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .project-item-title {
    display: block;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 28px;
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 36px;
    letter-spacing: -0.56px;
    color: #000;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    transition: color 200ms;
  }

  .project-item:hover .project-item-title {
    color: #707070;
  }

  .project-item-desc {
    display: block;
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 24px;
    color: #707070;
  }

  .project-divider {
    border: none;
    border-top: 1px solid #d0d0d0;
    margin: 0 96px;
  }

  .project-link {
    color: #000;
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 6px;
    transition: color 200ms;
  }

  .project-link:hover {
    color: #707070;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .article {
      padding: 0 24px 0;
    }

    .article:last-of-type {
      padding-bottom: 80px;
    }

    .article-hero {
      padding: 120px 0 64px;
    }

    .article-hero--sub {
      padding: 72px 0 48px;
    }

    .article-title {
      font-size: 36px;
      line-height: 44px;
      letter-spacing: -0.72px;
    }

    .article-body {
      margin-left: 0;
    }

    .article-body p {
      font-size: 20px;
      line-height: 30px;
    }

    .article-figure {
      margin: 40px 0;
    }

    .project-item {
      gap: 20px;
      padding: 28px 0;
    }

    .project-thumb {
      width: 128px;
      height: 85px;
    }

    .project-item-title {
      font-size: 22px;
      line-height: 28px;
      letter-spacing: -0.44px;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }

    .project-item-desc {
      font-size: 14px;
      line-height: 22px;
    }

    .project-divider {
      margin: 0 24px;
    }
  }
</style>
